column17: Over the last week, how often did you…

column16: …have a strong urge to do it?

column17: Over the last week, how often did you…

column16: ...picture times you did something like this in the past?
...imagine how good it would be to do it?
...imagine how much better you’d feel if you did it?
...imagine how much worse you’d feel if you didn’t do it?

column17: Over the last week, how often…

column16: ...did other things remind you about it?
... did thoughts about it grab your attention?
... did thoughts about it come to mind?
